{"tid":1850089,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"網上廣傳大量疫症假消息　蝙蝠宴片段源自帕勞非中國","createTime":"2020-01-29T11:11:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T11:34:00.000Z","uid":330582,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a5938d450673440ff3ddba23b91b8c15641729f2","tid":1850089,"uid":330582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:11:31.000Z","msg":"Now係味笑緊cctai班兒登仔無獨立思考能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】新型冠狀病毒在多國蔓延，相關的假消息傳播速度可能比疫情擴散更快，影響同樣不容忽視。多個社交網絡平台加強打擊疫情的不實資訊。<br />\n<br />\n新型冠狀病毒疫情爆發初期，網上已開始流傳多個「驚人」消息甚至陰謀論，例如指英國早在幾年前知悉這種新病毒，為疫苗申請專利，質疑有人蓄意「放毒」；又有人指，病毒源自中國秘密生物武器計劃，由實驗室外洩，或者用一種精油可殺死新型冠狀病毒。<br />\n<br />\n這些說法或有網紅「加持」，但全無事實根據。<br />\n<br />\n不少人相信都看過這個蝙蝠宴的片段，將疫情歸咎於中國人食野味，但其實這兒不是內地，而是太平洋島國帕勞。<br />\n<br />\n很多時被瘋傳的片段沒有註明來源或時間，很難證實真偽，一旦廣傳開去，更難以正視聽。<br />\n<br />\n多個社交網絡平台近日致力打擊不實疫情消息，Facebook、Google、Twitter、抖音國際版TikTok等有不同措施加強把關，希望杜絕假新聞散播，包括與事實查證機構合作，將搜尋連結到可信的網站，可惜假新聞始終禁之不絕。<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞一名男子涉嫌在網上散播疫情的假消息，周二被拘捕。新加坡政府引用《假新聞法》，追究一個不實報道新加坡有人死於新型冠狀病毒的網站，要求更正。<br />\n<br />\n在內地，《人民日報》和《環球時報》也懷疑發布假新聞，刊登一張資料圖片說是新建成的武漢火神山醫院。<br />\n<br />\n面對疫症威脅，人人自危，但抗疫需要智慧，種種假資訊隨時引發不必要恐慌，大家不應輕信或極速轉發未經查證的訊息，以免墮入散播謠言者的圈套。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=378508&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D378508%26refer%3DShare&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBH99ps0HX4IqOCTpD1RfAd9E%3D&h=9d56a4ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D378508%26refer%3DShare&h=ab0ef571\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=378508&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"7dce355b4fb92c96e3353cc4230cea765a7a4efe","tid":1850089,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:12:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />wfc</span>"},{"pid":"fa4605bda17a2aa12216638c236d3ed78e4aba03","tid":1850089,"uid":66719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:14:29.000Z","msg":"有智慧既人都知係P4室驗室洩漏"},{"pid":"cef539e4c08289c5d8b36ce86cdad0552054e50f","tid":1850089,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:28:24.000Z","msg":"Facebook/Twitter 都唔畀講係支共實驗室放毒，特登cump"},{"pid":"d03d17fd20a5dd006f366b527f89e8c5badecdd0","tid":1850089,"uid":191107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:29:38.000Z","msg":"我收到風連登係第一源頭添"},{"pid":"091d43970dd5e6678aa1153cf5e45dc27ad6967e","tid":1850089,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:32:17.000Z","msg":"帕勞講普通話？"},{"pid":"d349489194d9d6e965155948c5e0a61cb9298afa","tid":1850089,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:33:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/19A1dEE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F19A1dEE.jpg&h=8cddb755&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N4yRAS0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN4yRAS0.jpg&h=3e070cc0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dRr7TEG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdRr7TEG.png&h=1a06d4b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mEGf2yj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmEGf2yj.jpg&h=438cf0ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bacfabcf13c5fa6539a20bcab89e0f42dcfab4d7","tid":1850089,"uid":28547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T11:34:00.000Z","msg":"條片係講普通話既中國人食野味，<br />\n只不過係外國食，都係反映緊中國人既惡習。<br />\n地點唔係重點，唔會因為地點唔同就改變左個睇法。<br />\n我都有俾錢睇Now 新聞，真係好失望。<br />\n依家身邊有人唔當疫情嚴重，令我更加恐慌。"}]}